# nocache.cadish — importable sub-config.
# The ~50 `if (req.url ~ "...") return(pass)` VCL rules collapsed.
# `cadish check` would warn: "these 50 routes are 1 lookup, not 50 regexes".

@nocache path \
    /account/*  /publish/*  /upload-photo/*  /security-check/* \
    /order-error/*  /user-panel/*  /mailer/*  /videos/getvideo/* \
    /embed-video/*  /favorites/*  /sellers/*  /buy-credits/* \
    /private/*  /pub/*  /panel/*  /admin-area/*  /wallet/* \
    /buy/*  /transaction/*  /response/*  /payment-done/* \
    /payment-error/*  /media/image_server.php  *sitemap*

# Category listings: the EXCEPTION that IS cached (short TTL + grace).
# In the VCL this was an ugly nested if/else; here it is one named matcher.
@listings path_regex \
    /(catalog|deals|brands|electronics|\
      clothing|home-garden|toys|books|sports|grocery|\
      beauty|automotive|outlet)/
